General.Name: Compodium International AB
General.Description: Compodium International AB (publ), a technology company, provides digital collaboration solutions for organizations, companies, and authorities. The company offers Vidicue, an encrypted video communication solution that secures meetings with sensitive and classified information; and TDialog, a secure messaging solution. It also provides fulfillment, project management, consultancy, development and engineering, green recycling, and sustainability services. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Luleå, Sweden.
